      "role": "user",
      "content": "the curtain falling... that's a scary way to put it. but honestly, it sounds a lot more peaceful than this. like, if the show is over, i don't have to keep up the act. i don't have to keep pretending everything is fine when i feel so hollow. it's just exhausting to exist when you're not even really inhabiting your own life.",
